NAME

DateTime::Locale::rof - Locale data examples for the Rombo (rof) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Rombo locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Ijumanne, 5 Mweri wa kaili 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Ijumaa, 22 Mweri wa ikumi na mbili 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Ijumamosi, 15 Mweri wa tisa -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Mweri wa kaili 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Mweri wa ikumi na mbili 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Mweri wa tisa -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 M2 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 M12 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 M9 -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10
